Hi,

I believe an earlier post indicated that, since the analog inputs on the
expansion board are multiplexed to the analog input 0 on the HB, if you cut
the trace on analog port 0, the expansion board analog ports will all be
"pull-up resistor"-less. One cut trace, 8 pullup-less analog inputs.

